Creating The Dashboard Step By Step. 6

After understanding the the story about creating  the TSA Cost Per Claim Analysis Dashboard, now it is time to build your own dynamic dashboard that will look the same as my final dashboard.




In the next Slides we will explain in details, step by step the process of building this Dashboard.

Outline :

1) Download and load the data

2) Transform The Data

3) Create the tables relationship.

4) Create Dax Calculated Measures. 

5) Create The title and The Logo.

6) Create the slicers.

7) Create the Cards.

8) Create the KPIs.

9) Create "Cost per claim & YoY by Month" Chart.

10) Create "Cost per claim & YoY by Type" Chart.

11) Create "Cost per claim & YoY by Site" Chart.

12) Create "Cost Per Claim By Airport" Map.

13) Fix the Title of the Visuals.

14) Create YoY Pointer and Format YoY Color.
